Yes, you can wait for up to or more than an hour to get a table, Yes, when someone takes a number two in the bathroom and you are waiting on line, which happens to be right next to the bathroom, it can get pretty 'intense', Yes, you can wait up to or more than an hour to get a table (Did I already say that? :-) BUT the burgers really are so good, the McSorleys cost only $2.50 (ppl!!), and the ambience is perfect for catching up with a close friend. I highly recommend it! Worth waiting every time :-)
